<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Re:View - 통합 게시판</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style>
        .search-container { margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .search-container input { padding: 10px; width: 300px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .item-type-tag { font-size: 0.7rem; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 5px; display: inline-block; }
        .tag-note { background: #e3f2fd; color: #1976d2; }
        .tag-question { background: #fff3e0; color: #f57c00; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">Re:View</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/board">전체게시판</a>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/write">오답작성</a>
                    <a href="/profile">마이페이지</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/login">로그인</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <header style="margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center;">
            <h1>통합 게시판</h1>
            <p>오답 노트와 질문을 한곳에서 확인하세요.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="search-container">
            <form action="/board" method="GET">
                <input type="text" name="search" placeholder="제목 또는 내용 검색..." value="<%= search %>">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">검색</button>
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="notes-list">
            <% if (notes && notes.length > 0) { %>
                <% notes.forEach(item => { %>
                    <a href="<%= item.item_type === 'note' ? '/post/' + item.id : '/questions/' + item.id %>" class="card">
                        <span class="item-type-tag <%= item.item_type === 'note' ? 'tag-note' : 'tag-question' %>">
                            <%= item.item_type === 'note' ? '오답노트' : '질문' %>
                        </span>
                        <h3><%= item.title %></h3>
                        <p><%= item.content_text.substring(0, 80) %>...</p>
                        <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
                            <span>작성자: <%= item.username %></span>
                            <span><%= new Date(item.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %></span>
                        </div>
                    </a>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div style="text-align: center; padding: 50px; color: #999;">
                    검색 결과가 없거나 게시글이 존재하지 않습니다.
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
